
Installation step of mysql-server in ubantu
1. sudo apt-get update
2. sudo apt-get install mysql-server
3. after successfully installation
   sudo mysql
4. run select command for check root password is blank or not

   SELECT user,authentication_string,plugin,host FROM mysql.user;

5. for changing root password run below command.
   ALTER USER 'root'@'localhost' IDENTIFIED WITH mysql_native_password BY '12345';
   FLUSH PRIVILEGES;

6. then login mysql server by using
   sudo mysql_secure_installation
7. mysql -u root -p



